example_rename.prompt:
Please rename the following ERP item to be more descriptive and user-friendly while maintaining technical accuracy. The name should be clear and easy to understand for end users.

Original name: {erp_name}
Category: {category}
Subcategory: {subcategory}
Sublevel: {sublevel}

example_standardize.prompt:
Please standardize the following ERP item name to follow our company naming conventions. The name should be consistent with our existing product naming standards.

Original name: {erp_name}
Category: {category}
Subcategory: {subcategory}
Sublevel: {sublevel}

Please provide a standardized name that follows our conventions.

Underscored_names.prompt:
Standardize the following ERP item name to follow our company naming conventions. The name should be consistent with our existing product naming standards.

Original name: {erp_name}
Category: {category}
Subcategory: {subcategory}
Sublevel: {sublevel}

Provide a standardized name that follows this convention:
- Every name start with type (Screw, Pen, Motor)
- Second part of name is part number if applicable
- Third part is one or multiple descriptive parameters
- Name parts must be separated with "_" other space must be replaced with "-"
- If any part of the name can't be properly deduced use web search using original name
